description: This Chainlink VRF nut low Anurak purrs with a rating of 1, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 1, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, 8 for South, and 5 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20011-94853-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [1 Vote, Nut Low]
